---
title: Mediterranean-Inspired Grilled Beef Kebabs with Garlic Pitas and Summer Salad
description: Bring a part of the Mediterranean to your dinner table with tonight's grill recipe. Beef kebabs and garlicky pitas get kissed by the grill, then topped with a summery salad. A dollop of tzatziki adds a fresh, creamy finish to this easy and tasty dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/kebabs-de-boeuf-grilles-a-la-mediterraneenne-12d0884b.jpg
